Sep 23 2003	Great Hotel in Montreal	I travel frequently to Montreal for work and I have always stayed at Le Nouvel Hotel. The hotel is clean, the staff is very friendly. The rooms are large and the ones on the street side have a nice view. The hotel is centrally located in downtown Montreal. You can walk to the Bell Centre to catch a hockey game and you are only one block south of St. Catherine street which is the main shopping district. All in all in the hotel is very nice and one that I will continue to visit. I just wish they had hi-speed internet access in the rooms. They do have a business center with PC's that are connected to a broadband connection but their use is an additional fee.	
